def get_streetname(cell):
    for addr_part in cell.split(','):
        for s_type in ['', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '',
                      '', '', '']:
            if s_type in addr_part: return addr_part
    return cell.split(',')[1]

rest_data['streetname'] = rest_data['address'].apply(get_streetname)
rest_data['streetname'] = rest_data['streetname'].str.strip()
